  <title>
   <narrative xml:lang="EN">Local Cooperation Fund (LCF) in Burundi</narrative>
  </title>
  <description>
   <narrative xml:lang="EN">Overall objective is to increase participation of grassroots organisations and grassroots organisations and groups in the local debate on elections and governance issues in Burundi. Therefore, the project aims at training activists in ten local groups to become tutors of grassroots comics workshops and capable of running comics workshops independently after the training. Funds will be used to prepare Kirundi language training material on grassroots comics, arrange a tutor training workshop and  participants run test comics workshops</narrative>
  </description>
